      "body" : "I&#39;ve found a number of differences between the compilers handling of generics in difficult cases. Here are two I made questions about on here in case you want to add them to your answer:  <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/13501836/possible-java-compiler-bug-program-does-not-compile-with-some-compilers\" title=\"possible java compiler bug program does not compile with some compilers\">stackoverflow.com/questions/13501836/&hellip;</a>  <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/13980552/oracle-jdk-and-eclipse-jdt-compilers-disagree-which-is-compiling-this-incorrect\" title=\"oracle jdk and eclipse jdt compilers disagree which is compiling this incorrect\">stackoverflow.com/questions/13980552/&hellip;</a>"
